name: Lemmings 2 - The Tribes [SG]
description:
Lemmings 2: The Tribes is a puzzle game developed by Rockstar North and DMA Design. It was originally released in 1993. It was published by Psygnosis. The game is rated as "Recommended" on RAWG.
Lemmings 2: The Tribes is available on Game Boy, Atari ST, Commodore / Amiga and SNES.
